WEBVTT



00:01:02.520 --> 00:01:03.240
He got away.

00:01:03.639 --> 00:01:05.400
Looks like he hasn't been gone long.

00:01:06.919 --> 00:01:08.319
The laptop belongs to Wang Dongdong.

00:01:08.720 --> 00:01:09.400
That kid...

00:01:09.839 --> 00:01:11.239
Even on the run, he's still watching cartoons.

00:01:12.199 --> 00:01:13.040
Doesn't look like he was on the run.

00:01:13.559 --> 00:01:14.919
More like something happened.

00:01:15.519 --> 00:01:16.599
Or someone called him away.

00:01:18.080 --> 00:01:19.440
There's no sign of a struggle.

00:01:19.599 --> 00:01:20.559
Probably someone he knew.

00:01:21.279 --> 00:01:22.080
And...

00:01:24.959 --> 00:01:26.760
The footprints look like they were tampered with.

00:01:27.279 --> 00:01:28.360
You can't make out the shape.

00:01:32.919 --> 00:01:35.800
What's that round mark?

00:01:45.440 --> 00:01:47.279
Did you smell perfume?

00:01:53.959 --> 00:01:54.599
Didn't smell it.

00:01:56.120 --> 00:01:56.760
Didn't smell it.

00:01:56.760 --> 00:01:57.559
No.

00:01:58.040 --> 00:01:59.360
You've got a pretty sharp nose.

00:02:05.800 --> 00:02:06.760
Hello, Captain Duan.

00:02:06.919 --> 00:02:08.479
A new kidnapper just showed up.

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:09.960
The ransom doubled.

00:02:11.199 --> 00:02:12.279
A new kidnapper?

00:02:12.720 --> 00:02:13.720
And the ransom doubled?

00:02:21.199 --> 00:02:22.639
This time it's for real.

00:02:23.279 --> 00:02:25.199
Wang Dahai is panicking now.

00:02:25.559 --> 00:02:27.160
He's not yelling to drop the case anymore.

00:02:27.639 --> 00:02:28.919
Wang Dahai's got a lot of shady stuff going on.

00:02:29.360 --> 00:02:30.839
Could it be the thief crying "stop thief"?

00:02:31.639 --> 00:02:33.000
Then this father and son are unreal.

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:35.600
No.

00:02:36.720 --> 00:02:38.320
The marks here are too weird.

00:02:38.759 --> 00:02:39.919
The footprints are only half there.

00:02:40.479 --> 00:02:42.440
And there's a round imprint next to them.

00:02:49.240 --> 00:02:51.080
That round imprint...

00:02:51.679 --> 00:02:54.240
Could it be some kind of cane?

00:02:56.039 --> 00:02:58.160
And the perfume I smelled at the scene...

00:02:58.160 --> 00:02:58.720
Oh no!

00:02:59.320 --> 00:03:00.919
Wang Dahai's employees are making trouble.

00:03:08.479 --> 00:03:10.240
He told me to have dinner with the boss.

00:03:10.279 --> 00:03:11.240
The boss hadn't even said anything yet.

00:03:11.240 --> 00:03:13.000
You put your hand on my leg first!

00:03:13.000 --> 00:03:15.000
Wang Dahai, you damn liar!

00:03:15.000 --> 00:03:16.759
You said I'd be the next Jay Chou!

00:03:16.759 --> 00:03:17.399
All I had to do was come up with...

00:03:17.399 --> 00:03:19.039
200,000 for the debut fee.

00:03:19.039 --> 00:03:20.279
Then I'd debut and release an album!

00:03:24.119 --> 00:03:25.559
What's going on here?

00:03:29.800 --> 00:03:31.320
You're just leaving me like this, Dahai?

00:03:31.839 --> 00:03:32.720
Wang Dahai!

00:03:36.160 --> 00:03:36.960
Stop right there!

00:03:37.240 --> 00:03:37.720
Go!

00:03:46.759 --> 00:03:47.559
Wang Dahai!

00:03:48.600 --> 00:03:49.240
Stop!

00:03:49.240 --> 00:03:50.000
Wang Dahai!

00:03:51.360 --> 00:03:51.919
Don't run!

00:03:52.000 --> 00:03:52.639
Get him!

00:03:52.639 --> 00:03:53.240
Get down!

00:04:10.240 --> 00:04:11.080
How did the kidnapping news...

00:04:11.080 --> 00:04:12.320
...get out?

00:04:14.160 --> 00:04:15.839
Going on strike at a time like this...

00:04:16.559 --> 00:04:18.200
If nobody's behind it...

00:04:18.799 --> 00:04:20.079
I'll eat my hat, I'm telling you.

00:04:28.920 --> 00:04:30.119
Your hair tie fell off.

00:04:30.320 --> 00:04:30.839
Thanks.

00:04:31.959 --> 00:04:32.920
I didn't see Zeng Lili.

00:04:33.320 --> 00:04:33.839
Normally...

00:04:33.959 --> 00:04:35.079
She's a longtime employee too.

00:04:36.200 --> 00:04:37.000
Zeng Lili.

00:04:38.200 --> 00:04:39.200
This Zeng Lili...

00:04:39.320 --> 00:04:40.760
I always felt she and Wang Dahai were off.

00:04:45.720 --> 00:04:46.239
Sister Lili...

00:04:46.440 --> 00:04:47.519
She didn't come today?

00:04:50.600 --> 00:04:51.239
Let's go.

00:06:02.880 --> 00:06:03.519
Lin Shen.

00:06:09.720 --> 00:06:10.320
What is it?

00:06:10.880 --> 00:06:11.799
Whose room is this?

00:06:12.519 --> 00:06:13.239
Zeng Lili's.

00:06:13.600 --> 00:06:14.480
Is there a problem?

00:06:14.720 --> 00:06:15.440
Perfume.

00:06:15.880 --> 00:06:16.720
This is the scent.

00:06:17.239 --> 00:06:18.079
It's hers.

00:06:23.399 --> 00:06:24.320
Hello, Captain Duan.

00:06:25.000 --> 00:06:25.839
You two, get back here, now.

00:06:26.000 --> 00:06:26.839
The kidnapper called.

00:06:26.920 --> 00:06:27.559
The exchange is tonight.

00:06:30.839 --> 00:06:31.359
Captain Duan.

00:06:31.880 --> 00:06:32.600
Right now, Zeng Lili...

00:06:32.600 --> 00:06:33.679
...is highly suspicious.

00:06:33.880 --> 00:06:35.160
You two come back first.

00:06:52.119 --> 00:06:52.839
Dad!

00:06:53.399 --> 00:06:53.920
Son!

00:06:54.720 --> 00:06:55.399
Dad!

00:06:55.440 --> 00:06:56.720
Son!

00:06:57.239 --> 00:06:57.920
Dad!

00:06:58.359 --> 00:06:59.359
Save me!

00:06:59.519 --> 00:07:00.359
Dad's here.

00:07:01.559 --> 00:07:02.720
I brought the money.

00:07:03.440 --> 00:07:04.399
Where are you?

00:07:04.760 --> 00:07:05.679
Come out!

00:07:06.160 --> 00:07:07.239
Come out!

00:07:09.799 --> 00:07:10.760
What's the situation now?

00:07:11.880 --> 00:07:13.359
The ransom's been swapped for decoy money.

00:07:13.679 --> 00:07:14.359
What about the tracker?

00:07:14.359 --> 00:07:15.239
It's already been set up.

00:07:15.720 --> 00:07:17.040
But as the exchange time got close...

00:07:17.160 --> 00:07:18.720
Wang Dahai suddenly became unstable.

00:07:19.079 --> 00:07:20.119
He kept repeating...

00:07:20.519 --> 00:07:21.760
...that we have to save his son.

00:07:23.279 --> 00:07:23.959
Where are you?

00:07:24.200 --> 00:07:24.920
Come out!

00:07:37.519 --> 00:07:39.519
See that knife on the ground?

00:07:41.440 --> 00:07:42.480
You die...

00:07:43.359 --> 00:07:44.519
...your son lives.

00:07:45.440 --> 00:07:47.399
I don't want to die!

00:07:48.279 --> 00:07:49.640
Dad...

00:07:54.559 --> 00:07:55.200
Fine.

00:07:56.799 --> 00:07:57.839
A life for a life.

00:07:58.359 --> 00:07:59.239
All right.

00:07:59.799 --> 00:08:00.320
But...

00:08:00.720 --> 00:08:02.399
Let my son go first.

00:08:03.239 --> 00:08:04.839
Save me!

00:08:05.399 --> 00:08:07.839
I don't want to die!

00:08:08.359 --> 00:08:10.359
Dad!

00:08:10.839 --> 00:08:11.640
Dongdong!

00:08:12.359 --> 00:08:13.160
Son!

00:08:13.600 --> 00:08:14.160
It's okay.

00:08:14.320 --> 00:08:15.200
It's okay.

00:08:15.359 --> 00:08:15.959
Dad's here.

00:08:15.959 --> 00:08:16.519
It's okay.

00:08:16.920 --> 00:08:17.839
Dad's here to save you.

00:08:17.839 --> 00:08:18.399
It's okay.

00:08:18.399 --> 00:08:19.160
It's okay, son.

00:08:25.160 --> 00:08:25.839
Stop!

00:08:26.440 --> 00:08:27.559
Dad!

00:08:27.559 --> 00:08:29.079
Help me!

00:08:29.480 --> 00:08:30.720
No!

00:08:31.239 --> 00:08:32.880
Don't you like feet?

00:08:34.039 --> 00:08:35.359
Still like them?

00:08:37.119 --> 00:08:38.599
As long as you let my son go,

00:08:39.479 --> 00:08:40.840
I'll do anything.

00:08:40.840 --> 00:08:42.159
Anything you want.

00:08:42.159 --> 00:08:43.280
I brought the money.

00:08:43.679 --> 00:08:44.960
I can give you anything.

00:08:44.960 --> 00:08:46.280
Anything at all.

00:08:46.280 --> 00:08:47.280
Even my company.

00:08:47.280 --> 00:08:48.440
You can have that too.

00:08:52.599 --> 00:08:54.200
Dad!

00:08:54.440 --> 00:08:55.239
Please!

00:08:56.080 --> 00:08:56.840
I'm begging you!

00:08:57.400 --> 00:08:58.520
Let my son go!

00:09:02.359 --> 00:09:03.320
Let him go!

00:09:03.679 --> 00:09:05.880
Then when I begged you back then,

00:09:05.960 --> 00:09:07.960
why didn't you spare me?

00:09:08.919 --> 00:09:09.760
I was wrong.

00:09:10.000 --> 00:09:10.840
I was wrong!

00:09:10.840 --> 00:09:11.599
I deserve to die.

00:09:11.599 --> 00:09:14.000
I was wrong!

00:09:16.960 --> 00:09:17.960
Cut the crap.

00:09:18.280 --> 00:09:19.559
I want you dead.

00:09:19.559 --> 00:09:20.440
And your son lives.

00:09:20.440 --> 00:09:21.640
I want you dead!

00:09:21.640 --> 00:09:22.919
Did you hear me?

00:09:23.599 --> 00:09:24.239
Fine.

00:09:27.760 --> 00:09:29.440
As long as you let my son go,

00:09:30.320 --> 00:09:31.119
okay.

00:09:35.119 --> 00:09:36.039
This is insane!

00:09:36.320 --> 00:09:36.919
Move!

00:09:37.200 --> 00:09:37.880
Yes, sir!

00:09:48.039 --> 00:09:49.320
Keep your word!

00:09:50.960 --> 00:09:52.159
Let my son go!

00:09:52.960 --> 00:09:54.119
I can die.

00:09:56.479 --> 00:09:58.400
Dad!

00:10:14.200 --> 00:10:16.440
Let's go to hell together!

00:10:17.320 --> 00:10:17.960
Zeng Lili!

00:10:21.719 --> 00:10:22.400
Zeng Lili!

00:10:22.479 --> 00:10:23.359
Don't do anything rash!

00:10:35.479 --> 00:10:35.919
Guozi!

00:10:35.960 --> 00:10:36.520
Save him!

00:10:36.559 --> 00:10:37.320
Seal off the exits!

00:10:48.640 --> 00:10:49.440
Zeng Lili!

00:10:49.799 --> 00:10:50.520
It's over.

00:10:50.799 --> 00:10:51.559
Stop running.

00:10:52.760 --> 00:10:53.559
Zeng Lili!

00:10:55.960 --> 00:10:56.679
Zeng Lili!

00:11:00.000 --> 00:11:00.679
Lu Yi!

00:11:01.320 --> 00:11:02.039
Lu Yi!

00:11:07.119 --> 00:11:07.840
Come back first!

00:11:08.320 --> 00:11:09.000
Don't be impulsive!

00:11:09.760 --> 00:11:10.559
Turn back now.

00:11:11.119 --> 00:11:12.320
It's not too late for anything.

00:11:15.320 --> 00:11:16.440
Who said I was running?

00:11:24.359 --> 00:11:25.080
Zeng Lili!

00:11:36.119 --> 00:11:36.919
Lin Shen!

00:11:39.719 --> 00:11:40.640
Hang on!

00:11:45.599 --> 00:11:46.239
Lu Yi!

00:11:48.239 --> 00:11:48.960
I can't hold on!

00:11:56.159 --> 00:11:56.880
Lin Shen...

00:11:58.919 --> 00:12:00.239
You're my best friend.

00:12:00.919 --> 00:12:01.719
Listen to me.

00:12:02.559 --> 00:12:03.440
Hold on to me tight!

00:12:04.559 --> 00:12:05.440
Hold on!

00:12:08.039 --> 00:12:09.200
Hold on to me!

00:12:12.000 --> 00:12:13.080
Grab on!

00:12:38.159 --> 00:12:39.000
I should've known.

00:12:39.000 --> 00:12:40.200
You're a cop.

00:12:43.239 --> 00:12:44.440
So back then you

00:12:45.320 --> 00:12:47.440
acted arrogant on purpose to drive me off.

00:12:48.080 --> 00:12:49.440
You were really trying to protect me.

00:12:49.840 --> 00:12:50.640
Right?

00:12:53.440 --> 00:12:54.719
I just don't want anyone to become

00:12:54.719 --> 00:12:55.679
another me.

00:12:57.200 --> 00:12:58.880
You shouldn't have saved me just now.

00:13:01.760 --> 00:13:03.239
Even if it wasn't you who jumped today,

00:13:03.239 --> 00:13:04.119
and it was someone else,

00:13:05.159 --> 00:13:06.159
this idiot here

00:13:06.919 --> 00:13:08.520
would still save them without hesitation.

00:13:09.200 --> 00:13:10.159
You're not special at all.

00:13:10.159 --> 00:13:11.520
You know that?

00:13:15.200 --> 00:13:16.080
If

00:13:17.400 --> 00:13:19.080
this hadn't happened,

00:13:20.280 --> 00:13:21.400
we probably could've been

00:13:21.400 --> 00:13:22.719
really good friends.

00:13:28.919 --> 00:13:30.320
Actually, sometimes,

00:13:30.719 --> 00:13:32.440
friendship is like love.

00:13:33.119 --> 00:13:34.960
There's no room for a third person.

00:13:54.719 --> 00:13:55.559
Let's go.